upscale-video-tensorrt.name: Upscale Video with TensorRT
upscale-video-tensorrt.description:
Upscale a video using TensorRT. This is faster than the normal upscaler, but there are limitations:
* You can only upscale the input video by 4X.
* Input video width and height must BOTH be less than 1280.
